2024-10-23T13:51:54.732Z | 173.21.3.15  | 725447              | Connection error?      | "{""unmapped.nested"":""d"",""unmapped_event_duration"":""725449"",""unmapped_message"":""Disconnection error""}"
2024-10-23T13:52:55.015Z | 173.21.3.15  | 8268152             | Connection error?      | "{""unmapped.nested"":""c"",""unmapped_event_duration"":""8268154"",""unmapped_message"":""Disconnection error""}"
