// DROP an unmapped field by name (gap): the user explicitly drops the demand-loaded unmapped_message
// column; the intended correct behaviour also removes it from _unmapped_fields, because the DROP
// signals the user does not want the field anywhere in the output. Currently unmapped_message
// still appears in _unmapped_fields because DetermineUnmappedFieldsToKeep reads the ResolvingProject
// output and unmapped_message is not there (it was dropped), so no exclusion entry is added.
// This test documents the intended correct output; it will fail until the production gap is fixed.
dropUnmappedField
required_capability: optional_fields_load_all

SET unmapped_fields="LOAD_ALL"\;
FROM partial_mapping_sample_data
| DROP unmapped_message
| SORT @timestamp
;

